                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1665" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0051</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11873 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">破解VMI困境——天天物流公司打造供应链协调者新角色</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Solve the VMI dilemma——Tiantian logistics creates the new role of supply chain coordinator</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钱蓝，宋华明</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏州工业园区天天物流有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天天物流公司；供应链管理；第三方物流；供应商管理库存(VMI)；供应链协调者</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tiantian logistics company; supply chain management; the third-party logistics; vendor managed inventory; supply chain coordinator</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在第三方物流服务同质化竞争日趋激烈的今天，苏州天天物流公司开始思考如何用更专业的眼光优化客户优化供应链，用主动贴心、贯穿全程的物流服务来提升客户供应链管理水平，在为客户创造价值的同时实现第三物流的跨越式增长。本案例中，天天物流公司为供应链上下游企业新立公司和思康公司提供VMI物流服务。但是，通过库存数据的分析，天天物流公司发现VMI并没有真正降低客户供应链的整体库存，思康公司库存业绩的改善是以新立公司的库存业绩的恶化为代价的，VMI没有实现供应链成员的双赢。在为新立公司—思康公司的VMI服务中，如何从传统的被动物流服务提供者向供应链协调者的角色转换，为客户供应链提供专业的增值服务，破解VMI困境，提高客户供应链整体的绩效，实现VMI客户与第三方物流的真正意义上的共赢，成为摆在天天物流公司面前的一个迫切需要解决的问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Nowadays, with the pressures of the increasingly fierce homogenization competition of the third-party logistics services, Tiantian Co. tries thinking about how to optimize the customer and supply chain with a more professional perspective, how to improve the level of supply chain management with active and throughout service to create value for customers while the third-party logistics could grow by leaps and bounds. In this case, Tiantian Co. provides VMI logistics service for the supply chain upstream and downstream companies, i.e., Xinli Co. and Sikang Co.. Through analysis of inventory data, Tiantian Co. found that VIM did not reduce systematic inventory in supply chain. Meanwhile, improvement of Sikang’s performance is based on deterioration of Xinli’s inventory, and VMI did not bring a win-win situation to supply chain members. How to change the logistics service provider into supply chain coordinator, and how to provide more professional value-added services, through them solve VMI dilemma and improve the overall efficiency of the customer’s supply chain, realize win-win supply chain with VMI. The mentioned above problems are needed to be solved urgently for Tiantian Co..</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营与供应链管理》、《物流管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应商管理的库存</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-09</td>
                            </tr>
